sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as vLLM Orchestrator Gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detectors as Detector Services<br/>(e.g., regex-language)
    participant LLM as vLLM Inference Backend

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Detection
        Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8090/TCP | No TLS<br/>Auth: Authorization header
        Note right of Gateway: Injects detectors config<br/>from route definition<br/>(input/output detector maps)
        Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>HTTP or HTTPS 8085/TCP<br/>Auth: mTLS cert + forwarded Authorization
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run input detectors<br/>(e.g., PII regex scan)
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
        Orchestrator->>LLM: Generate chat completion
        LLM-->>Orchestrator: Generated response
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run output detectors
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: JSON response with detections
        Note right of Gateway: If detections found &<br/>fallback_message configured:<br/>replace response choices
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(original or fallback message)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,LLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion with Detection (SSE)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8090/TCP | stream: true<br/>Auth: Authorization header
        Note right of Gateway: Injects detectors config<br/>Sets stream: true
        Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>HTTP or HTTPS 8085/TCP (streaming)<br/>Auth: mTLS cert + forwarded Authorization
        Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run input detectors
        Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
        Orchestrator->>LLM: Generate streaming completion
        loop SSE chunks
            LLM-->>Orchestrator: SSE chunk (delta)
            Orchestrator-->>Gateway: SSE data: {...} chunk
            Note right of Gateway: Parse each SSE chunk<br/>Check for detections<br/>If detected: substitute<br/>fallback & set finish_reason: stop
            Gateway-->>Client: SSE event (original or fallback)
        end
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE [DONE]
    end
